Workflow Skill Router is a pre-execution Skill-selection layer for Codex. It
classifies work as Single, Phased, or Managed Goal work, discovers the
available capabilities, and selects the smallest sufficient Skill set without
replacing runtime permissions, approval policies, or tool access controls.

This standalone repository contains Plugin version `{{VERSION}}`, generated
from canonical source revision `{{SOURCE_REVISION}}`.

