## Install

Install the immutable release tag rather than the moving `main` branch:

```powershell
codex plugin marketplace add eric861129/workflow-skill-router-plugin --ref v{{VERSION}}
codex plugin add workflow-skill-router@workflow-skill-router-plugin
codex plugin list
```

The repository root contains the Plugin manifest, Skill, bundled MCP server,
and deterministic Python runtime needed at execution time. For install modes,
runtime boundaries, and troubleshooting, read the [canonical documentation](https://huangchiyu.com/Workflow-skill-router/).

## Validate

